1. Download the 'Controller' directory 

2. Go to the 'Controller' directory 
Eg.
>> cd /opt/Controller

3. Run the 'controller-config.sh' as below
>> ./controller-config.sh <Controller_IP_Address>
Eg.
>> ./controller-config.sh 192.168.0.2

4. This script will remove all the previous configuration (with database) and configures the nova services

